==Korean==
===Particle===
# grammatical markers 을 and 를 indicate the object of a Korean verb. They are postpositions, which come '''after''' the word they modify. (In English and French, prepositions come first, like ''to school'', ''de France''.)

If the modified word ends in a consonant, append 을, but if it ends in a vowel, append 를.

